This is a letter from President Donald J. Trump to the Speaker of the House, Nancy Pelosi. The letter is in accordance with a specific section of the Continuing Appropriations Act, 2020, and the Health Extenders Act of 2019. The President designates all funding, including the rescission of funds, for Overseas Contingency Operations/Global War on Terrorism. This designation is in line with the Congress' designation in the Act. The details of this action are provided in the enclosed memorandum from the Acting Director of the Office of Management and Budget.